  "description": {
    "en": "Herbal preparation derived from Muli. Made from crushed oyster shell, muli is salty, astringent and cool in nature, entering the liver and kidney channels. It calms liver yang, helping to relieve symptoms of sadness, insomnia and dizzines..."
